HEADWORD: Re-sign
<hw>Re-sign"</hw> <pr>(r?-s?n")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>re-</ets> + <ets>sign</ets>.]</ety> <def>To affix one's signature
